00:08:25.040 --> 00:08:32.600
When they asked Me what puja we should have in Vancouver,
I had heard about this ashram that it is placed

00:08:46.180 --> 00:08:53.180
in very beautiful surroundings of nature and,
as nature is being created by the power of

00:09:02.440 --> 00:09:09.440
Saraswati, I thought best would be to have
the Puja of Saraswati here. Another thing

00:09:12.880 --> 00:09:19.880
is that when people live in nature, they become
extremely creative, their delicate feelings

00:09:24.240 --> 00:09:31.240
are preserved and they are never in a rush;
or they are not what we can call too much

00:09:34.430 --> 00:09:41.430
modernized, because nature soothes them down.
So also the creativity of Saraswati adds to

00:09:46.180 --> 00:09:53.180
artist, and I knew that there must have been
many artist in this country created since

00:09:56.720 --> 00:10:00.190
long.

00:10:00.190 --> 00:10:07.190
The Canada as such I feel is the Hamsa Chakra
of the Vishuddhi, but the power of Saraswati

00:10:24.250 --> 00:10:31.250
becomes Mahasaraswati when it is manifested
by the Mahabrahmadeva which is called as Hiranyagarbha.

00:10:37.670 --> 00:10:44.670
For that She has to cross through the Hamsa.
She crosses through Hamsa and becomes the

00:10:46.170 --> 00:10:53.170
Vishnumaya Shakti. I mean She is the Vishnumaya
Shakti. So Saraswati becomes the Vishnumaya.

00:11:01.510 --> 00:11:08.510
She crosses at two points - one at Hamsa and
another at Vishuddhi - so She is the Sister

00:11:12.630 --> 00:11:19.630
of Shri Krishna. So Saraswati was born as
the Sister of Shri Krishna, and when Krishna's

00:11:25.370 --> 00:11:32.370
mama name whose was, uncle was Kamsa, he came
to kill Her, She just rose into the sky and

00:11:36.890 --> 00:11:43.890
became the lightning, and She declared the
coming of Shri Krishna, that He is already

00:11:48.310 --> 00:11:52.060
there existing.

00:11:52.060 --> 00:11:59.060
So the relationship between Shri Krishna and
Vishnumaya is that of a brother and a sister,

00:12:02.380 --> 00:12:09.380
and surprisingly the other day we celebrated
the Rakhi Bandhan, Raksha Bandhan, which is

00:12:11.880 --> 00:12:18.780
the same thing as the brothers/sisters relationship.
So now here we are celebrating actually the

00:12:18.780 --> 00:12:25.780
Deity which is the Sister of Shri Krishna.
Later on She was born as Draupadi, and that's

00:12:28.490 --> 00:12:34.580
why Shri Krishna went to save Her chastity,
because is the brother only who is concerned

00:12:34.580 --> 00:12:40.460
about the chastity and the name of the sister.

00:12:40.460 --> 00:12:47.460
So this is what yesterday happened that is
the Saraswati Puja, so Vishnumaya, Herself,

00:12:51.210 --> 00:12:58.210
yesterday sixteen times thundered here; and
I didn't tell anybody what was happening,

00:12:59.880 --> 00:13:06.880
but I knew She would do that. And apart from
that, She has also threatened Washington.

00:13:08.210 --> 00:13:14.800
That's a good thing because Washington has
to be awakened. Now these are very, very subtle

00:13:14.800 --> 00:13:21.800
things and very subtle relations, and only
I can tell these things because I know them,

00:13:23.820 --> 00:13:30.820
that these relations exist. So I was not surprised
that She was there, but exactly sixteen hundred

00:13:32.380 --> 00:13:39.380
times She passed it, this part of Vancouver,
is to show that the time has come for you

00:13:44.730 --> 00:13:51.730
to understand that Sahaja Yoga is so important,
and if we do not assert ourselves fully to

00:13:55.940 --> 00:14:02.940
Sahaja Yoga, Vishnumaya is going to take another
form which may burn all your forest, may burn

00:14:03.610 --> 00:14:10.610
everything. Now you must know that lightning
represents all the five elements in it - it

00:14:14.570 --> 00:14:21.570
has sound, it has light, it is in the ether,
it acts in the ether. Also it has got what

00:14:21.960 --> 00:14:28.960
you called the water in it, and when the water
goes into friction, which is the Mother earth,

00:14:33.940 --> 00:14:37.930
so all these things act through Her.

00:14:37.930 --> 00:14:44.930
