00:15:19.960 --> 00:15:26.960
kind, only thing whatever is created by Mother
Earth like swayambus, that's only we worship.

00:15:27.320 --> 00:15:33.490
And that, too, we worship now in a way that
is an abstract way, because wherever they

00:15:33.490 --> 00:15:39.490
