00:32:53.010 --> 00:33:00.010
here what you find very nicely boasting, "You
know, I have divorced my two wives, and this

00:33:01.630 --> 00:33:08.630
third one is coming up. You can meet her."
So that there's no shame about it, no shame,

00:33:08.890 --> 00:33:13.510
no feelings, nothing. I mean you married a
woman, you lived with her, she was your wife

00:33:13.510 --> 00:33:18.530
and you have no feelings for her. Your own
children also they have no feelings at all,

00:33:18.530 --> 00:33:22.890
no feelings. Of course they're not like English,
where the English people kill their children,

00:33:22.890 --> 00:33:28.080
so that's not so bad. But here I've heard
also they kill their husband, wife, kills

00:33:28.080 --> 00:33:33.230
each other and all that. And for what? For
love. When they do not have love for one husband,

00:33:33.230 --> 00:33:37.560
how are they going to have love for another
husband? I can't understand. Love is a quality

00:33:37.560 --> 00:33:38.610
of heart.

00:33:38.610 --> 00:33:44.970
So this is what it is - if you see the whole
character is numbed out because they don't

00:33:44.970 --> 00:33:49.790
behave like human beings. They behave like
- I don't know, again I say I don't know like

00:33:49.790 --> 00:33:56.400
who because there's no comparison whatsoever.
So it is not that only in America people are

00:33:56.400 --> 00:34:02.510
like that, it is all over. But in America
it is too much, too much of it, and all such

00:34:02.510 --> 00:34:09.510
things rise from America. All such funny notions
rise from America, and everybody takes them

00:34:10.100 --> 00:34:17.100
because they know how to advertise, they know
how to make it very, very popular.

00:34:20.760 --> 00:34:27.760
Once I was travelling by a ship and a pilot
came over the ship, and he was talking to

00:34:28.880 --> 00:34:33.920
Me and he told Me that his brother is a very
nasty devil.

00:34:33.920 --> 00:34:35.320
I said, "What happened?"

00:34:35.320 --> 00:34:42.240
So he said that he got hold of these four
boys who were Beatles, and he became their

00:34:42.240 --> 00:34:49.240
manager. And he started this music and got
some women, got them drunk, put them on the

00:34:50.300 --> 00:34:57.180
drugs. And the first music when they had that
music, these girls started screaming, shouting,

00:34:57.180 --> 00:35:03.250
going mad. And it become popular. Normally
the reaction would be that, "Ba, it's such

00:35:03.250 --> 00:35:08.340
a thing that when the music starts the girls
go mad, so don't go to such a music." On the

00:35:08.340 --> 00:35:13.460
contrary, so many started coming. How do you
explain this kind of a reaction? The more

00:35:13.460 --> 00:35:20.460
they shout, the more they scream, according
to them it's something. Means behind it is

00:35:21.330 --> 00:35:28.330
one thing that it has touched them somehow;
otherwise, why will they scream? Means such

00:35:29.200 --> 00:35:34.570
dumb people are been touched by something
is something great and all of us should go.

00:35:34.570 --> 00:35:39.910
We are also dumb, so we should attend to it.

00:35:39.910 --> 00:35:46.910
Now you may ask Me that "Mother how this dumbness
has come into people and this?" Is as simple

00:35:48.270 --> 00:35:53.870
as that as I told you, that they've used their
freedom to such an extent, their attention

00:35:53.870 --> 00:35:59.610
to such a wasteful pursuits, that they have
become really numb. Their attention doesn't

00:35:59.610 --> 00:36:06.610
feel anything. Attention when you put it out
it reacts, and it comes back to you as something.

00:36:06.910 --> 00:36:12.510
But if you all the time go on bombarding outside
your attention, this some bombardment from

00:36:12.510 --> 00:36:16.870
outside just finishes all your sensitivity.
There's no feeling, there's no attachment,

00:36:16.870 --> 00:36:23.870
there is no, no recording of anything that
is happening. So for that I think Vishnumaya

00:36:29.400 --> 00:36:35.860
is needed, and that's why She's placed on
the left side because Vishnumaya is the One

00:36:35.860 --> 00:36:41.750
in charge of people who have become absolutely
feelingless. That's why She's there to give

00:36:41.750 --> 00:36:43.000
you the feeling.

00:36:43.000 --> 00:36:48.960
So on the left side when She shines She gives
you the feelings, and people start understanding.

00:36:48.960 --> 00:36:55.960
So now the only thing that they have is a
kind of a mental idea that they're guilty,

00:36:56.680 --> 00:37:02.730
that's all. This is just mental. If it is
mental idea, "Oh, I'm guilty," then you are

00:37:02.730 --> 00:37:09.410
not going to feel it. I mean if you are, say
that you are mad, when you're not mad if anybody

00:37:09.410 --> 00:37:14.770
calls you mad you are not going to feel it.
It's like this. So they don't feel it at all

00:37:14.770 --> 00:37:20.700
because it is all mentally accepted thing
and they have become numb, "Now nobody can

00:37:20.700 --> 00:37:24.640
harm you, so what's wrong?" sort of an attitude.

00:37:24.640 --> 00:37:31.640
I would now ask you people to go all out and
become fiery, write in newspapers and say

00:37:31.790 --> 00:37:38.580
what's happening and how things are. I'm writing
a book like that now. It's called as Meta

00:37:38.580 --> 00:37:44.050
Modernism, and as far as I could be fiery
I'm going to be there to tell them what's

00:37:44.050 --> 00:37:51.050
wrong with them. And they should see to it
that this all wrong. No use trying to call

00:37:52.690 --> 00:37:57.800
it something great. Like now AIDS have come
up. I thought with AIDS, they will be awakened.

00:37:57.800 --> 00:38:03.050
So now the AIDS have become a martyrdom, now
yuppies came up.

00:38:03.050 --> 00:38:05.970
I said, "The yuppies will suffer from a disease."

00:38:05.970 --> 00:38:10.260
So now they said, "No, no, no, no. It's very
nice to be yuppies. After all you see they

00:38:10.260 --> 00:38:14.500
are another heroes who died for their yuppism."

00:38:14.500 --> 00:38:21.500
Like you see every stupidity is made into
a something kind of a very glorifying thing,

00:38:22.900 --> 00:38:29.350
so just - and people accept it. That's the
best part of it - they accept it. So it is

00:38:29.350 --> 00:38:34.620
important for you to be fiery, and to show
them in that light what they are. They have

00:38:34.620 --> 00:38:41.340
to be shown. It's not just a little light
of the Spirit will show them much, but it's

00:38:41.340 --> 00:38:48.340
the real dazzling, burning light of a lightening.

00:38:50.170 --> 00:38:57.170
So today's puja is going to be especially
for you all to develop that creativity of

00:38:57.860 --> 00:39:04.860
talking, behaving in every way in a fiery
way. That is going to put them right, nothing

00:39:06.130 --> 00:39:13.130
else. In creative work also when we create
something or we sing something and all that,

00:39:13.320 --> 00:39:20.320
if you go on singing say in our Indian style,
some music which is (Indian word) very slow

00:39:22.070 --> 00:39:28.300
talas, that won't go. They like somebody like
Ravi Shankar who just goes on mixing up notes

00:39:28.300 --> 00:39:35.300
and just goes on playing something which is
very, very unscientific according to Indians

00:39:35.380 --> 00:39:41.080
and is not at all entertaining. It doesn't
open your heart and something like that. But

00:39:41.080 --> 00:39:48.080
that is the thing that appeals to them, to
go into a big sort of a rock and roll sort

00:39:48.440 --> 00:39:53.220
- make it, sitar, into rock and roll, even
worse than that. I don't know the new latest

00:39:53.220 --> 00:39:55.200
one, I don't know what it is.

00:39:55.200 --> 00:40:01.110
So the second thing is that you can see how
they try to shock people. Also they try to

00:40:01.110 --> 00:40:06.240
shock people, because they know that they
are also like us. Like you go in the market

00:40:06.240 --> 00:40:13.240
you find somebody, his pant is - not pant
even, half pant - is all torn at wrong places,

00:40:14.240 --> 00:40:21.240
and it is just to shock people. They are supposed
to hear - at least they are supposed to, in

00:40:22.710 --> 00:40:27.870
America it is supposed to be you have to dress
up decently. You should not be indecently

00:40:27.870 --> 00:40:33.600
dressed. That's what they want, but what you
find whatever chance they can get to dress

00:40:33.600 --> 00:40:39.300
up in a way that you'll be shocked, they would
like to do. Like they have only one part of

00:40:39.300 --> 00:40:45.340
the hair as white. I mean anything, anything
is possible just to shock others, shock others

00:40:45.340 --> 00:40:51.730
and attract the attention. And what do you
get? Nothing. You spend so much money to attract

00:40:51.730 --> 00:40:55.700
the attention of others, but what do you get?
That attention doesn't give you anything,

00:40:55.700 --> 00:40:58.530
doesn't pay you anything, doesn't compensate.

00:40:58.530 --> 00:41:04.900
So it's such a joyless pursuit they get it.
All these things spoiled their attention which

00:41:04.900 --> 00:41:11.900
destroys to this extent that they're feelingless
people. They have no feelings left. And then

00:41:12.220 --> 00:41:19.220
the worse thing that has happened is they
become absolutely money-orientated. So the

00:41:20.630 --> 00:41:27.630
money is another side of Saraswati. Saraswati
is different from Lakshmi, so the Lakshmi

00:41:34.420 --> 00:41:41.420
and the Saraswati never go hand in hand. This
is the reason why when they get after Lakshmi,

00:41:42.960 --> 00:41:49.710
run after money too much, they get shocks.
Because there's a - suddenly you find stock

00:41:49.710 --> 00:41:55.050
exchange has fallen, there's a recession,
this business is gone, somebody who's very

00:41:55.050 --> 00:42:02.050
rich suddenly becomes a poor man. Is all the
work, this is all the work of the Saraswati.

00:42:04.290 --> 00:42:11.290
And if somebody is too much in Saraswati - reads
too many books, is an artist who is very ambitious,

00:42:14.490 --> 00:42:21.490
who tries to outshine other artist and all
that - such a person also gets back a reward

00:42:22.460 --> 00:42:28.630
from Lakshmi that his things never sell, he
never gets money, he starves, all sorts of

00:42:28.630 --> 00:42:29.020
thing.

00:42:29.020 --> 00:42:36.020
So these two things are in balance only in
Hamsa, or we can say they are in balance when

00:42:36.480 --> 00:42:43.480
you are Sahaja Yogi. So this has to be achieved
and is to be put together in balance that

00:42:45.890 --> 00:42:52.890
you have the blessings of the Saraswati as
well as that of Lakshmi. But it crosses only

00:42:53.480 --> 00:42:59.730
at the Hamsa point and at the Vishuddhi point.
So what do we have to do to bring the balance

00:42:59.730 --> 00:43:06.730
is that whatever we are earning, whatever
we are doing, we should not be in mediocre

00:43:08.190 --> 00:43:15.190
way. We should try to do it in a dynamic way,
in a fiery way. These two things should be

00:43:17.040 --> 00:43:24.040
combined at the Vishuddhi level. So now, supposing
you are going to give a lecture about Sahaja

00:43:27.080 --> 00:43:34.080
Yoga in a fiery way, and if you wear a dress
that you look like a hippie or somebody coming

00:43:34.450 --> 00:43:39.590
out of a jail, nobody is going to take you
seriously. But if you're properly dressed

00:43:39.590 --> 00:43:46.170
and you look respectable and presentation
is good, and then you give fiery speech, everybody

00:43:46.170 --> 00:43:53.170
is going to listen. So this principle of Lakshmi
Tattwa is to be used with the domination of

00:43:57.380 --> 00:43:59.180
the Saraswati principle.

00:43:59.180 --> 00:44:06.180
Now another blessings of Saraswati is that
you can have knowledge of Sahaja Yoga. I've

00:44:08.730 --> 00:44:15.730
seen many women especially in Sahaja Yoga,
they're Sahaja Yogis, their vibrations and

00:44:16.690 --> 00:44:23.690
all that is there, but they do not know what
is Sahaja Yoga. They do not know what these

00:44:26.130 --> 00:44:33.130
chakras are. They do not know that how these
vibrations go out. Now today's lecture is

00:44:33.740 --> 00:44:39.860
quite a lecture quite complicated I would
say, if you see to it. You have to listen

00:44:39.860 --> 00:44:44.710
to it at least four, five times to understand
it with the paper and a pencil. It's not an

00:44:44.710 --> 00:44:49.240
easy thing because I'm telling you now it's
all right, it's quite entertaining, but behind

00:44:49.240 --> 00:44:56.240
the entertainment there is a deep knowledge.
So I've not seen the Sahaja Yoginis mostly

00:44:57.200 --> 00:45:04.200
sit down with a paper and pencil to know what
is Mother saying, what is the knowledge She's

00:45:05.230 --> 00:45:12.230
giving us about the various things. To them
Sahaja Yoga means to be nice, to cook good

00:45:19.840 --> 00:45:26.840
food and help the Sahaja Yogis, just as come
to the pujas and all that and finished, also.

00:45:28.580 --> 00:45:34.360
So for them it is very important that they
should also know what is Sahaja Yoga. They

00:45:34.360 --> 00:45:39.190
must listen to My lectures, sit down, study
it nicely and understand it.

00:45:39.190 --> 00:45:46.190
The other way around are the men. For them
it is to do all the outside work, go round,

00:45:46.500 --> 00:45:53.500
see things and all that, But as far as relationships
are concerned, or as far as emotional side

00:45:58.480 --> 00:46:04.600
are concerned, they're negligent. And that
is why Sahaja Yoga by men is different; Sahaja

00:46:04.600 --> 00:46:10.770
Yoga by women is different. And in France
specially it has gone very far away from each

00:46:10.770 --> 00:46:15.030
other. The women were on one side, man are
on other side. Imagine in Sahaja Yoga you

00:46:15.030 --> 00:46:20.820
have such a nonsense as that, but then we
discover the person who was doing it and we

00:46:20.820 --> 00:46:26.710
managed it, so it was settle down and now
things are better. But women must know about

00:46:26.710 --> 00:46:32.730
Sahaja Yoga, but that doesn't mean that they
should fight with them, or think that they

00:46:32.730 --> 00:46:39.730
also know what these men know. But it's very,
very common. I've seen that men and women

00:46:40.270 --> 00:46:45.540
are having a different type of attitude towards
Sahaja Yoga. One is an extravert, another

00:46:45.540 --> 00:46:51.240
is an introvert. But in Sahaja Yoga there
is no difference between a woman and a man

00:46:51.240 --> 00:46:57.130
as far as knowing Sahaja Yoga is concerned.
I'm a woman Myself and I know so much, so

00:46:57.130 --> 00:47:00.920
why not the woman shouldn't know about what
is Sahaja Yoga?

00:47:00.920 --> 00:47:07.450
So all the women who are here or all over
have to know what is Sahaja Yoga. After all,

00:47:07.450 --> 00:47:14.450
look at Vishnumaya - She is a woman, is the
Power that works. Brahmadeva doesn't work.

00:47:14.880 --> 00:47:19.530
He's created all these things because He has
the Power of Saraswati, otherwise He could

00:47:19.530 --> 00:47:25.250
not have created. So everything is done through
the Power and the Power is a women, but if

00:47:25.250 --> 00:47:32.220
the Power doesn't know what is Sahaja Yoga,
how is She going to work it out? So the women,

00:47:32.220 --> 00:47:37.110
though they have children, I know - they have
to look after the household, kitchen - but

00:47:37.110 --> 00:47:43.940
it's such a pleasure, such a joy to read about
Sahaja Yoga, to understand it, to know it.

00:47:43.940 --> 00:47:50.270
Of course some of them do also read. I'm not
saying that they do not. But there are very,

00:47:50.270 --> 00:47:53.980
very few and they are very sensible, very
sensible.

00:47:53.980 --> 00:48:00.980
So this is My understanding of today's happening
that in this natural surrounding, these natural

00:48:02.880 --> 00:48:09.880
surrounding where we are blessed by the work
of Brahmadeva and Saraswati, and where we

00:48:10.810 --> 00:48:17.810
can feel the capacity of these Deities, to
what extent They can create. The nature is

00:48:19.410 --> 00:48:26.410
absolutely one with the Divine. Now see, as
soon as I came here the nature knew I'm there.

00:48:28.220 --> 00:48:32.780
It just started acting by itself. I didn't
have to give them a lecture, they didn't have

00:48:32.780 --> 00:48:38.240
to do a puja, nothing of the kind. They know
what I was doing. I went to Los Angeles, same

00:48:38.240 --> 00:48:43.350
thing. Anywhere I go the nature knows what
is to be done, "Now Mother is in the town,

00:48:43.350 --> 00:48:50.350
what should we do?" And they do it. So this
is the trouble, is that I have make you to

00:48:51.390 --> 00:48:56.490
do all kinds of deliberations for human beings
that "All right, do this, do that, do that."

00:48:56.490 --> 00:49:01.960
But I would say that spontaneously it should
happen, because now we are one. Just like

00:49:01.960 --> 00:49:08.070
the nature is one with Me, you are also one
with Me. And that should start happening when

00:49:08.080 --> 00:49:12.820
you will really become absolutely drawn into Sahaja Yoga, surrendered into Sahaja Yoga

00:49:12.820 --> 00:49:13.070
Now Saraswati is the Goddess of learning and
Mahasaraswati is the Goddess of knowledge,
you will really become absolutely drawn into Sahaja Yoga, surrendered into Sahaja Yoga

00:49:13.070 --> 00:49:15.900
you will really become absolutely drawn into Sahaja Yoga, surrendered into Sahaja Yoga

00:49:15.900 --> 00:49:21.160
then only it will happen. May God bless you.
